You can also create your own tournaments and take on your friends. Show everyone that you are the best with BePicks - Football Predictions!

PLAY WITHOUT RISKS
Bepicks is an application in which no real money is used. You can play without risks and with the possibility of winning incredible prizes.

OFFICIAL TOURNAMENTS
In official Bepicks tournaments you can win official football club shirts and selections, tickets for official matches, Amazon gift cards, official Bepicks kits, video games and much more.

WEEKLY CHALLENGES
Participate in our weekly challenges totally free and you can win cash prizes and special prizes. Each week you will have several opportunities to participate. Do not miss them !

CREATE YOUR OWN TOURNAMENT
With Bepicks you can create your own tournaments and have fun with your friends. Prove you're the best playing at BePicks without any risk!
Select the leagues you want to participate in the tournament. Invite your friends or teammates to the tournament. Configure your own game rules.
You have a ranking of players where you will see the position and the plays of each tipster.

UPLOAD LEVEL
The more you predict, participate and succeed in the app you will level up. After leveling up you will receive special chests loaded with direct prizes that will help you improve your performance in the app and even get direct gifts. Now you can sting with your friends and rivals for having the highest level in Bepicks.

ALL THE MOST IMPORTANT LEAGUES AND COMPETITIONS IN THE WORLD
Bepicks has the best leagues in the world and the most important national and international competitions. Play and predict in your favorite tournament with your favorite leagues: Champions League, LaLiga Santander, Premier League, Copa América, Europa League, Serie A, Argentine Super League, Bundesliga, Africa Cup, Ligue 1, Championship, Brasileirão, Liga MX, International Champions Cup, Eredivisie, Copa Libertadores, MLS, Russian Premier League, Movistar Peru Cup, Copa del Rey, Carabao Cup, European Super Cup, Spanish Super Cup, South American Cup, Libertadores Cup, Coupe de France, Trophée des Champions, UEFA Nations League, FA Cup ...

CALENDAR AND PARTY SCHEDULES
With Bepicks you can check the match schedule of any league or competition, as well as the match schedules and the TV channels where they are broadcasted.

STATISTICS
You have graphs and statistics to see the streak of successes and failures of any player in the app. Take advantage and learn from the best players by following their profile.

CHAT
Bepicks has general chat rooms and tournaments. Talk and share forecasts with your opponents. Discuss and make friends
